                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "A fine parcel. South-facing, well watered, poorly papered. Almost nobody holds clean title in this town - a detail, but details are my whole portfolio."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Company liaison. I verified a friendly competition down at the docks this quarter - and now I am verifying acreage. The region has such promising fundamentals. Whoever owns the ground under a thing owns the thing. Enjoy the fields while they are scenery."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Liaison — appraising the field",
                    Label: "default"
                },
                {
                    Priority: -1,
                    Buttons: [
                        {
                            Name: "That explains nothing",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "circle_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "The figure reflects standard verification adjustments. The adjustments are standard because they are applied to every figure, and the figure is correct because it reflects the adjustments. I am glad I could clarify this for you."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Liaison — standard adjustments",
                    Label: "no_explanation"
                }
            ]
